Keldling Bryg
This is a Brewolution all grain beer, supposed to reach 7,7%
alchohol, EBC 28 og IBU 20. It is more likely to be 7,0% alchohol.
Easter Egg: Dark candi sugar and dried orange peels!
Should possible be stored 3 - 6 months after end of carbonation
Saturday 5th of March 2016.
"Some things in life are bad / They can really make you mad" - "When you're chewing
on life's gristle / Don't grumble, give a whistle" - "If life seems jolly rotten / There's som
ething you've forgotten" - "When you're feeling in the dumps / Don't be silly chumps"
- "Always Look On The Bright Side Of Life" by Eric Idle
